title: Beautiful, Bright, Corner Unit, Lake View - On Lake Merritt in Oakland
posting_body: ['Looking for a bigger place with more room to move around, warmth, and amazing natural light?', 'Love the food, activities, and entertainment around Lake Merritt in Oakland?', 'Well, check out 1200 Lakeshore Apartments!', "We're glad to offer this large 2Bed, 2Bath home.", 'Floor to ceiling glass bathes the space in natural light throughout the 1,310square foot home.', 'You’ll love the views from the wrap-around balcony which adds 440 sqft of outdoor space and brings your total indoor-outdoor 1,750 sqft!', 'These building amenities make life more convenient:', '- FREE parking space with each apartment!', '- FREE water, sewer, garbage, and natural gas', '- 24-hour Package Lockers', '- 24-hour Security', '- 24-hour Laundry Facility', '- 24-hour Business Center', '- Mezzanine 4th floor has beautiful outdoor desert garden', '- Gym with dry saunas', '- Luxurious Community Room', '- Available Gigabit Fiber Internet', '- Just moments from Lake Merritt BART', 'To see current availability please visit us at <URL>', 'Please email or call to schedule your tour today!']
